      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STORM BREWING (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (20.59) in a Grade 5 at Traralgon. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Ready to return to form. TOMMY THE HOOD (8) doesn't win out of turn. Finished third (30.23) at Sandown latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can feature again. I'M EASY (3) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last five runs. Last start finished 2nd on July 5 over 350m at Healesville behind Son Of Rosie beaten 1.1 lengths (19.68) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Likely to be in the finish again. BIG DUKE (4) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
